A Map by Itsthomas

The dart bars for Santa Clara Valley Dart League

properties.name: Beefy's Cabin
properties.description: Posted by Itsthomas693 Grape Ave, Sunnyvale, CA 94087darts pub for Santa Clara Valley Darts Assn. This is an ideal setup for throwing darts. No food, but you can bring in stuff from local restaurants. Oh, and they only take cash at the bar (there\'s an ATM in the corner).

properties.name: Britannia Arms
properties.description: Posted by Itsthomas1087 De Anza Blvd, San Jose CA 95129darts pub for Santa Clara Valley Darts Assn. Obnoxious kareoke starts promptly at 10pm on Thursdays no matter who\'s in da house (you\'ve been warned)

properties.name: Duke of Edinburgh
properties.description: Posted by Itsthomas10801 N Wolfe Rd, Cupertino, CA 95014Darts pub in Cupertino. Santa Clara Valley Darts Assn plays out of here. The reining champs of our Division (B) play out of here. Not the friendliest setup for throwing (narrow alley, hard-to-see chalk board), but it\'s got old-pub character, and the bangers are divine.

properties.name: Fibbar Magee's
properties.description: Posted by Itsthomas156 S Murphy Ave, Sunnyvale, CA 94086Darts pub for Santa Clara Valley Darts Assn. Home to Level Pegs (my team!). Jackie\'s behind the bar every Thursday and is the best damn barkeep around.

properties.name: Katie Bloom's
properties.description: Posted by Itsthomas 369 E Campbell Ave, Campbell CAgreat bar in downtown Campbell. Parking can be difficult, but do-able (check near the library)
